songs.title: No Service
songs.lyrics:
[Refrain]
Dive off the roof, they yellin' suicide
I can't decide, I do two at a time
You say you gotta go to work girl what you mean
You like to chase so you pretend like you tryna leave
It's cool with me

[Verse 1]
Put that phone back in your bag
No service in the hills where we at
Got the shrooms, moon and the tabs
This a night that you ain't gettin' back

[Chorus]
It's 5 A.M., don't wanna leave
You changed your plans to be with me
The simple things, that's all we need
Get lost with me

[Refrain]
Dived off the roof, they yellin' suicide
I can't decide, I do two at a time
You say you gotta go to work girl what you mean
You like to chase so you pretend like you tryna leave
It's cool with me

[Verse 2]
Purple Rain playing in the back
It feels like the haze where we're at
Look up at the sky, take a drag
Tell your friends that you ain't gettin' back

[Chorus]
It's 5 A.M., don't wanna leave
You changed your plans to be with me
The simple things, that's all we need
Get lost with me
Get lose with me, babe

[Chorus]
It's 5 A.M., don't wanna leave
You changed your plans to be with me
The simple things, that's all we need
Get lost with me
Get lose with me, babe
